text: Besnik Musaj (born 29 December 1973) is a former Albanian cyclist who represented his country in the 1996 Summer Olympics. He competed in the men's road race, but he failed to finish the race.Sports-Reference Profile ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Albanian people stubs Category:1996 Summer Olympics stubs Category:Summer Olympics competitors for Albania
